+ EFFECT +
Action for giving/removing player effects.
Action type: Player
Usage: EFFECT <MODE> <PLAYERS> <EFFECT> [INTENSITY] [DURATION]


Arguments:
<mode>
  Required: YES
  Type: String (Message/Text)
  The mode (GIVE, REMOVE)

<players>
  Required: YES
  Type: Player List
  The players to affect.

<effect>
  Required: YES
  Type: EffectType
  The effect to give or remove.

[intensity]
  Required: NO
  Type: Byte (Whole Number, 0-255)
  The intensity of the effect, between 0-255. Variables are supported. Defaults to 1.

[duration]
  Required: NO
  Type: Int (Whole Number)
  The duration of the effect, or no duration for a permanent effect. Variables are supported.
